  "panoptic.adm.help_sum": "§7Manage which Panoptic tools are available to each player. All changes take effect immediately without requiring players to reconnect.",
  "panoptic.adm.help_b1": "In the «Groups» tab, you can configure permission sets. The default group applies to all players automatically, and you can create custom groups to fit your server's needs.",
  "panoptic.adm.help_b2": "In the «Players» tab, you can assign a player to a group or individually allow or deny specific permissions.",
  "panoptic.adm.help_b3": "The «Export» button copies the entire permission configuration to the clipboard, making it easy to transfer to another server using the «Import» button. The permission configuration is stored in the mod's server config.",
  "panoptic.adm.help_b4": "If your server uses LuckPerms, you can grant the `panoptic.admin` permission through it, allowing the player to access this interface.",
  "panoptic.adm.help_b5": "The default group applies to every player until they are assigned to a different group.",
  "panoptic.adm.help_b6": "Each player permission has three states: 'Dash' — inherits the permission from the group; 'Checkmark' — allowed; 'Cross' — denied.",

